notes_translated.fr: Il fournit de l'information sur la façon dont le Ministère compte appuyer le gouvernement pour la réalisation de notre programme au cours de l'année qui vient.
notes_translated.en: It provides information on how the Agency will support the Government on achieving our agenda in the coming year and I am fully confident that the Agency is prepared to successfully support me and work with our partners inside and outside government to deliver for Canadians.
